WEBVTT

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:11.720
You'll support me?

00:00:12.919 --> 00:00:14.240
We don't need to rush.

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:14.960
Are you out of your mind?

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:15.480
We can take it slow.

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:16.079
Get off.

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:19.000
We can take our time.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:19.600
Qiqi.

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:20.480
Scoot over a bit.

00:00:20.679 --> 00:00:22.440
I haven't gotten in yet, Qiqi.

00:00:24.120 --> 00:00:25.760
You look kinda familiar to me.

00:00:33.799 --> 00:00:35.079
I believe Wang Ping.

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:36.479
He did love me.

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.200
That's why he bought insurance in advance.

00:00:39.679 --> 00:00:42.079
So that I could collect the payout.

00:00:43.079 --> 00:00:45.520
I invested that money.

00:00:45.759 --> 00:00:46.799
What I earned

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.399
was enough for the rest of my life.

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:50.359
If only life

00:00:50.759 --> 00:00:53.359
could've stayed this peaceful forever.

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.439
Then why did you marry Wang Kechen?

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:58.840
I guess I was just starved for love.

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:00.479
This pigeon looks good.

00:01:00.479 --> 00:01:01.039
Try some.

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:01.600
Alright, alright.

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:02.280
Your favorite.

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:03.000
This one

00:01:03.399 --> 00:01:05.239
is made by the old Cantonese chef here.

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:05.840
Have a taste.

00:01:07.879 --> 00:01:08.480
Good, right?

00:01:09.519 --> 00:01:09.920
Delicious.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:11.319
I'm telling you, their Cantonese food

00:01:11.319 --> 00:01:12.359
is really exceptional.

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:17.920
Whether it was Qian Peng

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.760
or Wang Ping,

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.000
I truly loved them both.

00:01:27.159 --> 00:01:28.000
If only my days

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:31.680
could've stayed peaceful.

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:35.879
Until I met Wang Kechen.

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:39.920
He was witty and funny,

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:41.959
and really understood women.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.000
When he was courting me,

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:47.319
he'd buy me anything I wanted.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.079
I left home young,

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:52.760
so I deeply yearned for a family.

00:01:53.719 --> 00:01:54.879
It's kind of funny,

00:01:56.439 --> 00:01:58.239
but I love the smell of kerosene.

00:01:58.239 --> 00:02:00.040
He scoured the whole city

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.840
to find me an old kerosene lamp.

00:02:02.319 --> 00:02:03.599
I said I wanted to get married,

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:05.560
and he gave me a huge diamond ring.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.439
He even threw me

00:02:07.599 --> 00:02:09.080
a magnificent wedding.

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.120
A top-tier man like that,

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:13.439
what woman could possibly resist?

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:23.680
If you loved him so much,

00:02:24.159 --> 00:02:25.039
why did you want him dead?

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:30.039
There's a saying.

00:02:30.039 --> 00:02:31.960
I wonder if you two have heard it.

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:34.120
The dopamine rush of love

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:36.000
lasts only three to six months.

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.120
After that, it slowly fades away.

00:02:38.479 --> 00:02:39.680
Wang Kechen was special.

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.400
When you didn't love him,

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:42.960
his love would surge.

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:44.639
But the moment you fell for him,

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:47.199
his fading phase would begin.

00:02:47.439 --> 00:02:48.919
Then he'd slowly fall for someone else.

00:02:49.479 --> 00:02:50.400
Your assessment

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:52.000
is fairly objective.

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:54.439
Everyone thinks

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:57.319
I married him for money.

00:02:57.919 --> 00:03:01.080
But I'm the one he loves most now.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.039
Don't worry.

00:03:02.719 --> 00:03:04.479
I lost interest in him long ago.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.240
If you have the time,

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:07.439
you'd better deal with

00:03:07.439 --> 00:03:09.280
that womanizing husband of yours.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:10.960
You married him

00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:12.960
for the money, didn't you?

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:20.360
Don't tell me it was for true love.

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:22.759
I suggest you just get over it.

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:25.680
For money, you'd naturally tolerate it all.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.039
But I...

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:37.000
All I wanted was love and security.

00:03:39.199 --> 00:03:40.039
He took me...

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:42.759
He took me to his old flame's resort

00:03:42.759 --> 00:03:44.719
to celebrate our anniversary.

00:03:44.719 --> 00:03:46.599
It was an insult to me.

00:03:47.639 --> 00:03:48.400
I endured it.

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:51.039
Right in front of me,

00:03:51.039 --> 00:03:52.919
he chased after pretty young girls.

00:03:52.919 --> 00:03:54.000
I endured that too.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.039
But he said I

00:03:56.039 --> 00:03:58.319
was just a passing phase in his life,

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:01.240
and he'd leave all his money to his daughter.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.599
I couldn't take it anymore.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.039
I was completely done with him.

00:04:08.639 --> 00:04:09.719
I switched out his medication.

00:04:11.919 --> 00:04:13.639
Whenever his condition flared up,

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:16.199
it would look like an accidental death,

00:04:17.879 --> 00:04:19.360
having nothing to do with me.

00:04:26.959 --> 00:04:28.680
You had so many other choices,

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.120
yet you picked the worst one.

00:04:34.079 --> 00:04:35.759
I had no family to fall back on.

00:04:37.319 --> 00:04:39.600
I was just a pawn that hadn't crossed the river.

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:44.120
No support, no way back.

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:46.680
I could only rely on myself.

00:04:48.319 --> 00:04:49.639
What you've always wanted

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:50.800
is simply a sense of security.

00:04:51.920 --> 00:04:54.040
But that can only be found within.

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:56.079
When you seek it from outside,

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:57.879
it's all in vain.

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:00.560
Love is just one part of life,

00:05:01.839 --> 00:05:02.800
not all of it.

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:06.000
Everyone understands this.

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:07.759
But who

00:05:09.879 --> 00:05:11.079
can actually live by it?

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:13.399
I believe everything you've said is true.

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:15.959
But you're still hiding one thing.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:18.639
According to our investigation,

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:21.240
when you met Wang Kechen,

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:22.879
Wang Ping was still alive.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.800
Was his death really an accident,

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:27.160
or was there more to it?

00:05:27.839 --> 00:05:28.639
Officer Qin,

00:05:30.959 --> 00:05:32.240
You saw right through

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:33.839
my little tricks.

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:35.800
So I'll just tell the truth.

00:05:37.959 --> 00:05:38.600
That's right.

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:42.279
When I met Wang Kechen,

00:05:42.279 --> 00:05:43.639
my heart was already wandering.

00:05:43.639 --> 00:05:45.160
I was set on leaving Wang Ping.

00:05:45.879 --> 00:05:46.759
Who would've thought

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:48.879
he'd end up bringing about his own death?

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:50.279
For me,

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.199
it was at most

00:05:52.839 --> 00:05:53.839
failing to save him.

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:57.600
For so-called love,

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.639
you'd disregard a life?

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:01.079
Yes.

00:06:04.120 --> 00:06:05.439
That's the kind of person I am.

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:11.920
Tell them

00:06:16.279 --> 00:06:17.560
I'm willing to donate my kidney

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:21.720
to my brother.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.560
Boss Bai, don't you worry.

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:37.160
I'll reason with Qiqi.

00:06:37.439 --> 00:06:39.279
I'll get you two reconciled in no time.

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:44.199
It's not Qiqi I'm worried about.

00:06:44.439 --> 00:06:45.959
The resort is finished.

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:47.800
That can't be true.

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:50.639
How many days without any income?

00:06:53.759 --> 00:06:55.399
Who would vacation at a place

00:06:55.399 --> 00:06:57.079
where people keep dropping dead?

00:06:57.759 --> 00:06:59.560
The papers are full of it now.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:02.040
Our rooms are all empty.

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:04.160
The resort can't hold on much longer.

00:07:04.639 --> 00:07:05.959
If the resort goes under,

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:09.839
I'll have no choice but to shut it down.

00:07:10.879 --> 00:07:11.800
Then what do we do?

00:07:12.759 --> 00:07:13.160
I...

00:07:15.279 --> 00:07:17.160
I just became general manager!

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:20.120
Honey-trap rings aren't just two people.

00:07:20.319 --> 00:07:22.199
Do you have any handlers or accomplices?

00:07:22.439 --> 00:07:24.399
If I rat someone out,

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:25.839
can it count

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:28.040
towards a reduced sentence?

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.639
Of course.

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.040
The more you confess,

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.399
the better it'll be for you.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.879
Actually, A-Qiang and I

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:40.519
didn't start out doing this.

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.839
A-Qiang got into gambling

00:07:43.079 --> 00:07:44.560
and ran up loan-shark debts.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.120
There's this guy named Ma Xiaojun

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:49.480
who forced us into the honey-trap scam.

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:51.000
That guy...

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:52.920
he's vicious.

00:07:53.639 --> 00:07:54.800
I also heard

00:07:57.759 --> 00:07:58.879
he's killed people before.

00:08:00.279 --> 00:08:00.879
Boss,

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:03.399
this painting's an antique.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:04.800
You really want it down?

00:08:05.319 --> 00:08:06.199
What antique?

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:08.439
It's just an inkjet-printed knockoff.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:10.079
A painting this unlucky,

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:11.879
take it down.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.319
So if the painting is fake,

00:08:15.199 --> 00:08:16.519
then the Bai brothers' story

00:08:17.319 --> 00:08:18.279
is fake too.

00:08:20.439 --> 00:08:20.839
Here.

00:08:23.279 --> 00:08:23.800
Easy now.

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.079
Slow, slow, slow.

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:28.720
Wait,

00:08:29.439 --> 00:08:31.920
what... what is this?

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:34.799
This is the Bai family heirloom.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.360
Real or fake,

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.679
only I know.

00:08:39.720 --> 00:08:41.039
Take it to my office.

00:08:53.879 --> 00:08:54.240
Boss.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.000
Where is this?

00:08:57.279 --> 00:08:58.360
With the money I had left,

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.080
I took over this farmhouse restaurant.

00:09:00.799 --> 00:09:01.399
Yu Tianfang,

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:03.120
if you're willing,

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:05.200
you'll be the manager here from now on.

00:09:07.159 --> 00:09:07.720
Boss Bai,

00:09:07.919 --> 00:09:08.919
of course I'm willing!

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:10.639
You're the only one in this world

00:09:10.639 --> 00:09:12.399
who truly appreciates my talent.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:13.639
Don't worry.

00:09:13.639 --> 00:09:14.600
I'll definitely work hard.

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.000
In the future,

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.480
I'll make this place

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.519
the best

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:20.000
farmhouse restaurant in the city.

00:09:24.919 --> 00:09:25.480
Boss,

00:09:25.879 --> 00:09:26.360
look,

00:09:26.840 --> 00:09:27.960
right at this spot,

00:09:28.919 --> 00:09:30.320
let's have Siqi

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:32.440
keep performing here.

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:34.600
Things are tough now,

00:09:34.799 --> 00:09:36.120
but that doesn't mean they'll stay that way.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:36.960
I believe

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:39.200
we'll definitely make a comeback.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:40.519
Right.

00:09:40.519 --> 00:09:41.639
Set up the drum kit here.

00:09:41.639 --> 00:09:43.440
Siqi can keep performing here from now on.

00:09:43.879 --> 00:09:44.440
Boss Bai,

00:09:44.919 --> 00:09:45.720
don't worry.

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:48.320
Qiqi will definitely understand your good intentions.

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:49.960
Make way, make way.

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:52.080
Old Li,

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:53.039
you came too?

00:09:53.679 --> 00:09:55.679
You still owe me 20 bucks from cards last time.

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:57.879
Be careful!

00:09:58.519 --> 00:10:00.559
Don't go breaking my Qiqi's instruments.

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:01.480
Let me carry it.

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:02.759
You're so careless.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:05.919
Boss.

00:10:06.799 --> 00:10:07.279
Xiao Liu.

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:07.879
Look at that,

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:09.480
that kid's showing off again.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.000
He's young,

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.519
but full of schemes.

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:14.200
A young man willing to do extra work,

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:15.159
that's a good thing.

00:10:15.399 --> 00:10:16.480
Everyone has their flaws.

00:10:16.799 --> 00:10:17.960
I did a fortune reading today.

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:19.360
That kid Yu Tianfang

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.919
is a born jinx.

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:22.919
Wherever he goes, trouble follows.

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:24.759
Even your huge resort

00:10:24.759 --> 00:10:25.799
went bankrupt because of him.

00:10:26.519 --> 00:10:28.440
And you're bringing him to the restaurant?

00:10:28.440 --> 00:10:29.759
That's too unlucky.

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:31.440
You're talking nonsense now.

00:10:31.919 --> 00:10:32.679
I don't believe in that stuff.

00:10:32.879 --> 00:10:33.679
Think about it.

00:10:34.519 --> 00:10:35.960
Didn't the resort's business

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:38.200
start going downhill after

00:10:38.440 --> 00:10:39.279
he brought Xiaomao in?

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:42.080
Xiaomao hurt people over unrequited love.

00:10:42.639 --> 00:10:44.720
That kind of cursed bond is dangerous.

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:46.480
Ordinary people can't handle it.

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.360
You're just blaming him by association.

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:50.960
I only hire on character and ability.

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:52.240
Besides,

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:53.519
those who did evil

00:10:53.639 --> 00:10:54.919
have already been punished.

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:55.679
The past

00:10:55.879 --> 00:10:56.679
is not to be brought up again.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:57.879
Yu Tianfang

00:10:58.399 --> 00:11:00.919
took bribes behind your back at the resort

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.559
and hit on your daughter.

00:11:02.559 --> 00:11:03.159
Boss,

00:11:03.879 --> 00:11:06.120
he's stabbing you in the back!

00:11:12.399 --> 00:11:13.919
Started up a new business so quickly?

00:11:14.799 --> 00:11:16.200
Boss Bai, you're really something.

00:11:16.559 --> 00:11:17.639
Show some respect.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:19.720
I told you to keep it private before,

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:21.320
but now everyone knows you're my daughter.

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:22.320
If you keep acting like this,

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:24.039
what will people think of us?

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:25.240
I didn't come here to

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:26.600
play a loving mother-daughter act.

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:29.039
I kept trying to mortgage the resort,

00:11:29.159 --> 00:11:29.960
but you wouldn't agree.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:30.759
Now look,

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:31.960
we've lost everything.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:35.039
I hear

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.000
you got my real dad's inheritance.

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:37.879
Hand it over now,

00:11:38.039 --> 00:11:39.159
and we'll be even from then on.

00:11:39.159 --> 00:11:40.440
Wang Kechen's will

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:42.120
states I manage the inheritance.

00:11:42.120 --> 00:11:43.440
Once you're mature and responsible,

00:11:43.759 --> 00:11:44.600
I'll naturally give it to you.

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:47.399
You really think

00:11:47.559 --> 00:11:48.960
I'm just after that inheritance?

00:11:49.919 --> 00:11:51.240
I want revenge on you.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:54.120
You kept me from knowing my real father.

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:56.840
And he missed me too!

00:11:57.759 --> 00:11:58.159
Right.

00:11:59.159 --> 00:12:00.440
Read the contract carefully.

00:12:01.279 --> 00:12:02.879
The one we revised last time,

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.240
the payment terms,

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.039
go over it one more time.

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:09.519
How did my kite fall in the water?

00:12:10.679 --> 00:12:11.240
Hey, kid!

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:13.639
Kid!

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:15.120
Kid!

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.519
You can't climb over the railing!

00:12:17.519 --> 00:12:18.279
That's so dangerous!

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:20.039
My kite fell in the water, mister.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:21.559
Don't worry, I'll fish it out for you.

00:12:22.879 --> 00:12:23.440
Let me use this.

00:12:29.519 --> 00:12:29.879
Easy now.

00:12:29.879 --> 00:12:30.360
Thanks.

00:12:32.039 --> 00:12:32.759
Got it.

00:12:34.399 --> 00:12:34.879
There.

00:12:36.879 --> 00:12:37.320
Look,

00:12:37.799 --> 00:12:38.799
it's covered in weeds.

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.720
Shorten the kite string a bit.

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:42.159
Thank you, mister.

00:12:42.519 --> 00:12:43.320
Don't run too fast!

00:12:43.679 --> 00:12:44.399
One, two.

00:12:44.960 --> 00:12:45.919
Stay safe!

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:48.279
Don't climb the railing if it falls in!

00:12:50.360 --> 00:12:51.240
I didn't expect

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:52.759
you to be so kind, mister.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:53.960
You know,

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:55.799
I once had a cute, pretty daughter too.

00:12:56.440 --> 00:12:57.360
Unfortunately,

00:12:58.799 --> 00:13:00.559
I split up with her mother later on.

00:13:00.759 --> 00:13:02.200
I've never seen my daughter since.

00:13:04.159 --> 00:13:05.039
She should be

00:13:05.519 --> 00:13:06.679
about your age now.

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:07.799
So,

00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:10.799
do you miss your daughter?

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.240
If there's another life,

00:13:15.639 --> 00:13:17.200
I'll be a good father for sure.

00:13:18.279 --> 00:13:19.960
I'll be there as she grows up.

00:13:24.159 --> 00:13:25.240
When I was little,

00:13:25.799 --> 00:13:27.039
every year on my birthday,

00:13:27.399 --> 00:13:28.960
my wish was to see my dad.

00:13:29.159 --> 00:13:29.960
But in the end,

00:13:30.399 --> 00:13:31.720
he never came.

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:37.279
You have to believe

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:39.120
your father loves you, no matter what.

00:13:41.360 --> 00:13:41.960
He really does.

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.159
Mister, I gotta get to work. See you.

00:13:57.639 --> 00:13:59.200
I raised you for over twenty years.

00:13:59.200 --> 00:14:00.440
Am I really worth less than

00:14:00.440 --> 00:14:01.799
that deadbeat dad who never cared for you?

00:14:02.399 --> 00:14:03.679
Do you have any conscience at all?

00:14:04.159 --> 00:14:04.960
Is that inheritance

00:14:04.960 --> 00:14:06.759
worth more than our mother-daughter bond?

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:09.639
You still don't realize you're wrong.

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:11.840
You just want to seize the inheritance.

00:14:12.120 --> 00:14:13.840
You'd even steal from your own daughter.

00:14:14.039 --> 00:14:15.480
And you call yourself a mother?

00:14:17.159 --> 00:14:17.759
Qiqi.

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:19.279
Sit down, let's talk.

00:14:19.279 --> 00:14:20.279
What's mine is mine.

00:14:20.559 --> 00:14:21.399
Nobody can take it from me.

00:14:21.759 --> 00:14:23.080
Wait for the court summons.

00:14:27.840 --> 00:14:28.519
Qiqi!

00:14:40.320 --> 00:14:41.000
Qiqi.

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:42.519
Qiqi.

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:43.960
We're all family.

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:44.919
Come on, stop this.

00:14:44.919 --> 00:14:46.279
Yu Tianfang, who do you think you are?

00:14:46.279 --> 00:14:47.440
Stay out of our family business.

00:14:47.559 --> 00:14:48.279
Qiqi.

00:14:48.279 --> 00:14:49.480
Call me Qiqi again and I'll smack you.

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:51.200
Hey beautiful, need a ride?

00:14:51.559 --> 00:14:52.279
Twenty bucks.

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:54.000
No. Get lost.

00:14:54.000 --> 00:14:55.480
Hard to catch a cab this time of night.

00:14:55.759 --> 00:14:57.120
You won't get another chance like this.

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:58.600
Where you going? I'll take you.

00:14:59.200 --> 00:15:00.039
I've got my own car.

00:15:00.919 --> 00:15:01.919
If you really want to suck up to me,

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:03.759
wait till you can afford a Hermes belt.

00:15:03.759 --> 00:15:04.480
Then we'll talk.

00:15:14.679 --> 00:15:15.519
Whoa, watch out!

00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:16.440
Look out!

00:15:21.879 --> 00:15:22.679
Are you okay?

00:15:23.120 --> 00:15:23.559
I'm fine.

00:15:29.480 --> 00:15:31.919
Honey! Honey! Honey!

00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:36.440
Call an ambulance, quick!

00:15:37.200 --> 00:15:38.360
Call an ambulance!

00:15:39.279 --> 00:15:40.799
Honey, hang in there!

00:15:41.759 --> 00:15:42.320
Hello?

00:15:42.559 --> 00:15:43.360
Hello! Help!

00:15:43.519 --> 00:15:44.360
Help!

00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:45.440
Help me!

00:15:49.120 --> 00:15:49.600
Hello?

00:15:50.039 --> 00:15:50.559
Chufeng,

00:15:51.159 --> 00:15:52.679
someone just tried to run Siqi over.

00:15:53.279 --> 00:15:54.200
The car took off.

00:15:54.759 --> 00:15:55.519
Get here quick!

00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:57.279
Honey!

00:15:57.759 --> 00:15:58.480
Look at this.

00:15:59.039 --> 00:16:00.360
The restaurant hasn't even opened,

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:01.320
and trouble's already here.

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:03.200
Jinx! He's a jinx!

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:06.840
Honey!